# CI/CD Automation for Dockerized Applications Using GitHub Actions

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates the implementation of a Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) pipeline for a Dockerized Portfolio Website using GitHub Actions and Docker Hub.

The workflow automatically builds a Docker image and pushes it to Docker Hub whenever changes are pushed to the main branch.

---

## Objective

The objective of this project is to automate the Docker image build and delivery process using GitHub Actions, ensuring faster, reliable, and consistent deployments.

